,Recommended,319550,19325226,"Posted: 27 November, 2015",all,Acald25,"I got a coupon earlier today for making a badge. At first, I didn't think much since most coupons are for games that are of poor quality. When I saw the generous 90%, though, i investigated. Thank goodness I did! The 30 cents I put on this game have been the most satisfying 30 cents in my life. Heck, If I knew this game existed I would have paid full price for it. It is a clever game, resembling one of those old arcade games. The only difference is, you don't have to pay to play again. Its 3 dollers flat, and you can go on and on. No in game purchases to give you boosts, the only boosts you get are the ones you earn in the game. The controls are utterly easy to learn, the senstivity slider is a good implimcation. I also like the leaderboard, because it gives you a goal to set a distance. I love the music, and the graphics though simple make the game pleasant to look at. There are no bugs or concerns. Its a perfect 30 cents spent for me. If your buying this, and you like time killing games that trap you in a world of flying between holes at light speed, then 3 bucks would also be worth it.FInal statement: A clever, and suprisingly visually and mentally pleasing game. (Don't forget the music!)Totally worth the small price, I can picture myself tommorow spending some decent time continuing to train my reflexes and precesion on this wonderful game. Totally reminds me of one of those old arcade games. Very good job!"
