76561198005605242,Recommended,319550,13034318,"Posted: 21 November, 2014",all,roon,"Surprisingly engaging game, good for longer sessions and as a break from other, more sofisticated titles. Sensation of speed is taking you over quite early and it holds onto you for a whole duration of the game.As far as mechanics go, game is very simple - you just manouever with your mouse to avoid hitting the obstacles while velocity increases. No clicking or keys involved. Just a movement, that's what this game is all about after all. And it's really engaging.Graphics and sound are very minimalistic and raw - if you liked aesthetics of TRON movies, you will feel right at home with this one.All in all, I like this game very much."
